//|     A   -   source matrix, MxN submatrix is copied and transposed|
//|     IA  -   submatrix offset (row index)                         |
//|     JA  -   submatrix offset (column index)                      |
//|     A   -   destination matrix                                   |
//|     IB  -   submatrix offset (row index)                         |
//|     JB  -   submatrix offset (column index)                      |
