//|     N   -   size of matrix A.                                    |
//|     IsUpper -   True, if the matrix is upper triangular.         |
//|     IsUnit  -   True, if the matrix has a unit diagonal.         |
//| Result: 1/LowerBound(cond(A))                                    |
